item.title: [danlentz/clj-uuid "0.2.0"]
item.description: A Clojure library for generation and utilization of UUIDs (Universally Unique Identifiers) as described by RFC-9562. This library extends the standard Java UUID class to provide true v1, v6, v7 (time based) and v3/v5 (namespace based), and v8 (user customizable) identifier generation. Additionally, a number of useful utilities are provided to support serialization and manipulation of these UUIDs in a simple, efficient manner.
